{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC05_KEI_050.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x1e,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15e,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Umm, next, I put in the extract... Hmm, I wonder how much I should put in..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15f,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, my intuition is telling me maybe about as much as the amount of milk I drink in the morning..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15f,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Or maybe the amount of tea I drink at lunch? Hmm..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15f,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "I feel it's more like the tea and not so much the milk...I think."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x160,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Okay, this is starting to get scary, but I should just go with my gut and put it in."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "I'm coming in... Hmm, so you're synthesizing..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "What!? Mr. Keith!<CR>Did you stop by to play!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x13,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Of course not... How many years do you think we're apart in age?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x15,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Since I came to town to check out the bazaar, I decided to come see how you were doing."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "H-Hold on just a moment. I'll bring you some extract right away!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xe1,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "What in the world are you trying to make me drink?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Oops, I meant tea. I was just thinking about synthesis, and..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xe4,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Don't mind me. I didn't come here for a social visit."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xe7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "I'll be leaving soon enough."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Y-You're going home already? But you just got here."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x124,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Okay, then teach me one thing! I just came across something I don't know..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x91,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Don't substitute me for a text book...<CR>But it's useless to even say that,<CR>isn't it?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "I'm sorry. There's no one else I can ask. So..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "This book says to pour in the proper amount of extract...but I don't know how much is proper."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x93,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "You have to experience the general sensation. It's not something you can ask others."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "I understand that, but I've been<CR>studying on my own this whole time,<CR>so I don't have a sense of standards."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x15,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "Hmm..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x13,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "Well, it looks like you're not having any problems so far."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "Oh, is this okay...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "Yes, it's a normal reaction. In fact, you're doing pretty well."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "With the correct reaction, the liquid will turn this color. Remember that."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "O-Okay. And I have other questions that have been piling up like a mountain that I wanted to ask you..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xe1,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "Goodness... I thought it was going to be just \"one thing.\""
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xe3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "I guess I have no choice...<CR>I'll stay here a bit longer.<CR>In that case, I'll have some tea."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x34,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "Oh...yes! I'll pour you some right away!"
        }
    ]
}